00:43:57.730 --> 00:44:00.570
Things would've been precarious if not for Kasuhara-san's sister.

00:44:00.570 --> 00:44:03.170
She apparently rushed down to save him unconsciously

00:44:03.170 --> 00:44:05.750
when she noticed him off the trail.

